  "title": "Enrichment Hour",
  "description": "From the director of Rat Academy, come support the Calgary Zoo/Wilder Institute in a brand new initiative to give all the zoo animals a spot on an open mic. Zookeeper Chelsea has brought a variety of animals to perform many acts, from standup comedy to poetry to 'ponderings' on the nature of reincarnation.",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Three Cheese<br><strong>Director</strong>: Joseph McManus<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Marlo Hepburn, Ciarán Volke, Joseph McManus<br/></br>",
  "website": "https://instagram.com/threecheeseinstitute",
  "plain_language": "Enrichment Hour is about a zookeeper named Chelsea who is hosting a variety show open mic for zoo animals from the Calgary Zoo. The animals express themselves through poetry, comedy, song, and even a slapstick brawl. At the end of the hour, the audience will find out exactly how these animals feel about life, love, and reincarnation.",
